<author>mạjd ṣbḥy, mạjd ṣbḥy</author>
<title>lyk kl ạlạ̹krạm</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 ạlqrạr- lyk kl ạlạ̹krạm wạlạḥtrạm mlky ạlwḥyd
 qlby bygẖny yrfʿ lyk ngẖmạt tsbyḥ
 lḥn ạlmdyḥ lyk ạ̹nt wḥdk yạ mjyd
 1- bạlrwḥ wạlḥq bạsjd lyk
 fy̱ ḥḍwrk ʿyny̱ tbqy̱ ʿlyk
 jạyẗ bạʿln kl kẖḍwʿ qlby̱ lmlkk yạ yswʿ
 yạ ạ̹lh ạlậlhh yạ sydy̱
 2- yạ yswʿ bạrkʿ ʿnd rjlyk wdmwʿ ạlḥb ạ̉qdm lyk
 kẖd mkạnk ạlḥqyqy fy ʿrsẖ qlby yạ yswʿ
 yạ ḥyạẗ ạlqlb yạ mʿny̱ ạlḥyạẗ</lyrics>
</song>